<p>The Love Island beauty has recently returned from an enviable European break to St Tropez and Spain. </p>

<p>She had been making the most of the eased lockdown restrictions during her recent breaks as she partied alongside pals and relaxed on the beaches. </p>

<p>Francesca was spotted cosying up to a new man during a boozy night out in London last month. </p>

